so, just

```bash
# my.py
import numpy as np
def mm(A, B):
    return np.dot(A, B)
def mt(A, B):
    return np.dot(A, B.T)
def tm(A, B):
    return np.dot(A.T, B)
def tt(A, B):
    return np.dot(A.T, B.T)
```

```python
# my.pythran
mm(float[][], float[][])
mt(float[][], float[][])
tm(float[][], float[][])
tt(float[][], float[][])
