### Issue Description
This is question.
The calculation method of Invalid Depth Band is written in [realsense D400 series data sheet](https://www.intel.com/content/dam/support/us/en/documents/emerging-technologies/intel-realsense-technology/Intel-RealSense-D400-Series-Datasheet.pdf) (pp.55-56).
I calculated according to this. But, It seems smaller value than actual invalid area on the depth image.

Is my calculation wrong? What do you think?
